From: Ronan Abhamon <ronan.abhamon@vates.tech>
Date: Tue, 22 Apr 2025 11:10:24 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] chore(.github/workflows): use ubuntu-24.04

Previous version is no longer available.

Signed-off-by: Ronan Abhamon <ronan.abhamon@vates.tech>
---
 .github/workflows/main.yml | 4 ++--
 dev_requirements.txt       | 4 ++--
 2 files changed, 4 insertions(+), 4 deletions(-)

diff --git a/.github/workflows/main.yml b/.github/workflows/main.yml
index d89b968c..015d6412 100644
--- a/.github/workflows/main.yml
+++ b/.github/workflows/main.yml
@@ -23,14 +23,14 @@ jobs:
           mypy .
 
   build:
-    runs-on: ubuntu-20.04
+    runs-on: ubuntu-24.04
 
     steps:
       - uses: actions/checkout@v3
       - name: Set up Python 3
         uses: actions/setup-python@v4
         with:
-          python-version: '3.6'
+          python-version: '3.x'
 
       - name: Install dependencies
         run: |
diff --git a/dev_requirements.txt b/dev_requirements.txt
index f25f7686..5fbd5907 100644
--- a/dev_requirements.txt
+++ b/dev_requirements.txt
@@ -1,5 +1,5 @@
 coverage
-astroid==2.3.3
-pylint==2.4.4
+astroid
+pylint
 bitarray
 python-linstor
